To reach those goals you’ve got to be willing to play all the angles meticulously. From the relationship status between @JacobAndCo and Bugatti Rose gold and white diamonds baguette 💎🔥

The case is inspired by the flowing lines of the Chiron and the movement, or “engine block,” intended to duplicate the Bugatti engine, is placed under a massive sapphire crystal, on display for all to see. With the push of right-hand crown of the timepiece the engine comes to life, just like a true internal combustion engine. 
The movement is set with a total of 578 exquisite components. 
Right now Jacob’s workshop is doing something no one has ever even attempted before: to seamlessly combine engines and watches💯

node.text:
Sergio Ramos of PSG football club spotted at Stade de France with his son Alejandro wearing the gorgeous 18k white gold Patek Philippe Nautilus 5712G. The grey embossed dial shows hours, minutes, small seconds, date, moonphase and a power reserve indicator.
⌚️tag price: $52,500.00
•
📸 @vertigo1983

node.text:
Introducing the all new @jacobandco Twin Turbo Furious Sapphire Crystal, the first and still only watch in the world that incorporate a minute repeater inside a sapphire crystal case. The watch comes in three models differentiated by a Neoralithe chapter ring that surrounds the dial of each watch: one in red, one in green and the other in blu Bugatti. The sapphire crystal case provides a full view of the complex machinery of the Twin Turbo Furious that combine of a twin accelerated triple axis sequential tourbillon, a decimal minute repeater, a monopusher chronograph & the power reserve display.
Higher performance on the wrist with a total of 832 components in the movement and another 88 in the case. 
Each model is a unique piece priced at $ 1,500,000.00
